Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.87,0:00:05.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Raita{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}! Hatsune{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!\NCongratulations on your marriage!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.53,0:00:10.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, even if you congratulate us now,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.86,0:00:15.37,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,the wedding's not until tomorrow,\Nso we're not really married yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.19,0:00:18.20,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Hatsune Kamon (37)\NBride
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.19,0:00:18.20,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Raita Bamba (37)\NGroom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.37,0:00:18.21,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,It's fine, it's our wedding eve,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.21,0:00:22.31,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,and straight after the wedding's over\Nwe're flying off on our honeymoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.31,0:00:23.81,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.81,0:00:26.58,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Hey, you two! I'm jealous!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.58,0:00:29.22,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Hi! It's been so long, Mouri.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.22,0:00:32.34,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Then, is he that great detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.34,0:00:36.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yup, a bad friend from high school,\NKogorō Mouri.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.39,0:00:38.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you, I'm Hatsune.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.81,0:00:39.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.44,0:00:43.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And so the two next to you are your...?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.18,0:00:45.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm his daughter, Ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.97,0:00:48.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I'm Conan, a freeloader.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.37,0:00:51.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because of some reasons,\Nwe're looking after him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.05,0:00:54.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard you fell in love at first sight, is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.53,0:00:58.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we felt it was fate from the moment we met.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.35,0:01:00.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As if we'd finally found each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.70,0:01:05.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In any case, our birthdays, blood types and histories are the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.63,0:01:10.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sometimes, even if we're silent\Nwe can tell what the other is thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.69,0:01:12.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.72,0:01:15.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.75,0:01:16.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.97,0:01:19.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ugh! It's stuck to my trousers.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.11,0:01:22.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh... You're stepping on the cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.43,0:01:26.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry.\NToday is my first day here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.44,0:01:31.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. Could you bring a cloth to wipe his trousers?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.67,0:01:33.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure! I'll go get one.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.06,0:01:38.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, just because that waiter's hot\Ndoesn't mean you should go ogling him.{irome again xD I can't remember what we used last time}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.91,0:01:40.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why, are you jealous?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.66,0:01:42.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.22,0:01:44.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You haven't changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.00,0:01:46.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Still quick to get involved with women,\Nbut jealous when they do the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.68,0:01:47.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What're you going on about?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.67,0:01:52.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri, you're the one who used to\Nsend anyone who courted Eri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} flying.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.13,0:01:53.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-What about it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.59,0:01:54.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.90,0:01:56.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.13,0:01:59.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll never understand why men\Nalways want to monopolise women.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.94,0:02:01.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh? Where're you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.28,0:02:03.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The nail salon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.83,0:02:06.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To get the nail tips for the wedding put on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.93,0:02:09.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told you, you don't have to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.76,0:02:11.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's pouring with rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.42,0:02:13.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way, I've even got a reservation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.96,0:02:17.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the salon's staff are all\Nwomen, so you don't need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.93,0:02:20.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like I told you,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.63,0:02:22.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I won't forgive you\Nif you go having an affair.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.95,0:02:26.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's my line, "husband."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.35,0:02:34.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll be back in 2 hours,\Nso look out for my fingertips!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.24,0:02:34.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.18,0:02:40.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She should do it just before the wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.01,0:02:42.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She'll have to take them off before she goes to sleep tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.35,0:02:46.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, usually nail tips\Ngo for 24 hours without being taken off.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.57,0:02:49.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even when you have a bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.05,0:02:49.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.25,0:02:53.45,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Hehe... being a woman sounds like it's tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.15,0:03:00.03,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Vivid summer memories surpass their season to solve mysteries!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.03,0:03:04.20,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}An unbelievable car explosion strikes a couple on their wedding eve!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.20,0:03:05.95,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.95,0:03:08.00,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.00,0:03:10.41,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.01,0:05:00.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's my last night as a bachelor
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.58,0:05:03.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so be a bit kinder to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.51,0:05:06.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Bamba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, won't your wife get angry?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.00,0:05:13.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, he's still at it\Neven though he has a beautiful wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.15,0:05:15.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He really is just like a certain {\i1}someone{\i0} here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.93,0:05:19.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, mister.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.27,0:05:24.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ugh, you again. What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.14,0:05:26.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your phone's been ringing\Nfor a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.69,0:05:28.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.77,0:05:33.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, an e-mail from Hatsune.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.01,0:05:36.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"You won't pick up, so here's an MMS with my nails."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.24,0:05:36.29,Signs,,0,0,0,,You won't pick up, so here's an\NMMS with my nails. In 30 mins\Nyou can see them for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.29,0:05:36.33,Signs,,0,0,0,,You won't pick up, so here's an\NMMS with my nails. In 30 mins\Nyou can see them for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.33,0:05:36.37,Signs,,0,0,0,,You won't pick up, so here's an\NMMS with my nails. In 30 mins\Nyou can see them for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.54,0:05:36.58,Signs,,0,0,0,,You won't pick up, so here's an\NMMS with my nails. In 30 mins\Nyou can see them for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.55,0:05:39.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"In 30 minutes you can see them for yourself."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.58,0:05:36.62,Signs,,0,0,0,,You won't pick up, so here's an\NMMS with my nails. In 30 mins\Nyou can see them for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.62,0:05:39.12,Signs,,0,0,0,,You won't pick up, so here's an\NMMS with my nails. In 30 mins\Nyou can see them for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.12,0:05:41.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aww, you're already head-over-heels in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.40,0:05:42.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, well, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.61,0:05:44.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.63,0:05:47.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I've gotta go to the toilet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.00,0:05:47.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See ya...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.88,0:05:50.76,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Hmm? A second phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.46,0:05:53.40,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He's scowling while talking with someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.10,0:05:58.43,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Huh? He hung up straight away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.10,0:06:01.57,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Then went straight to the toilet...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.80,0:06:06.82,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Does that mean whoever phoned him is in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.82,0:06:09.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.34,0:06:10.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you see someone you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.80,0:06:12.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.78,0:06:15.40,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Well, I can't do anything anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.41,0:06:20.20,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Sanji Haruoka (48)\NCustomer
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.20,0:06:23.30,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Don't tell me he's the one who phoned him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.18,0:06:25.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Waiter!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.22,0:06:25.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.63,0:06:28.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.11,0:06:29.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bourbon, on the rocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.93,0:06:31.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.26,0:06:33.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Be more careful, you moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.01,0:06:34.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.72,0:06:40.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait a sec, Bamba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}. You're drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.14,0:06:41.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm fine, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.05,0:06:44.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, waiter!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.75,0:06:45.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.52,0:06:47.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you remember my order?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.98,0:06:50.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, bourbon, on the rocks, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.50,0:06:52.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, there's no mistake.{would've deliteralised, but I'm taking this line as a command to Tooru and to Bamba, which needs it to be this way :}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.71,0:06:53.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.20,0:06:58.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Bamba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, what're you scowling at?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.75,0:07:00.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.40,0:07:02.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.20,0:07:07.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This party's also Uncle Kogorō's class reunion, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.05,0:07:11.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, seems like the bride's wedding party was on another day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.93,0:07:14.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Though mum was busy with work and couldn't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.55,0:07:19.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then that guy with the sunglasses is one of your classmates?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.08,0:07:21.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.90,0:07:23.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't remember him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.31,0:07:25.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, it's been 20 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.40,0:07:27.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.90,0:07:43.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello. Yes, that's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.50,0:07:47.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes... yes, and?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.21,0:07:50.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.38,0:07:58.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey! What're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.80,0:08:02.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This customer suddenly threw a punch at me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.70,0:08:03.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.07,0:08:04.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't touch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.93,0:08:06.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Bamba.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.67,0:08:09.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You really {\i1}are{\i0} drunk, Bamba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.05,0:08:10.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, your hand's bleeding...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.70,0:08:12.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.74,0:08:15.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It won't be fine!\NYou've gotta get it treated...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.15,0:08:17.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bamba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, are you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.28,0:08:20.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only one I want to talk to now is Hatsune.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.03,0:08:25.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Hatsune. Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.05,0:08:28.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? "Goodbye"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.99,0:08:30.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What're you saying, Hatsune?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.72,0:08:33.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Hatsune! Hatsune, where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.01,0:08:37.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.84,0:08:40.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It can't be... that car's Hatsune's...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.89,0:08:42.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,- What?!\N- Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.31,0:08:45.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran! Call a fire engine,\Nan ambulance and the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.31,0:08:46.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.10,0:08:48.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hatsune... Hatsune...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.37,0:08:53.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hatsune! Are you okay?! Hatsune?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.49,0:09:01.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hatsune!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.68,0:09:07.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The corpse is charred,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.26,0:09:14.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so we're having their teeth compared with medical records, but I think the deceased is probably the car's owner,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.22,0:09:16.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hatsune Kamon{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.34,0:09:20.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it true that just before the car burst into flames,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.07,0:09:23.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,there was a phone call from\NKamon{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} implying it was suicide?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.22,0:09:23.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.82,0:09:24.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.72,0:09:30.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are two large travel suitcases in the car boot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.06,0:09:34.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those had probably been\Nprepared for their honeymoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.74,0:09:40.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The woman who died was going to be married to an old friend of mine tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.11,0:09:44.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why would someone so happy commit suicide?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.01,0:09:48.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who knows. Could it have been something like marriage blues?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.35,0:09:50.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Detective Takagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.02,0:09:53.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! You're in the way again...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.10,0:09:54.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.84,0:09:56.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't this a stick-on nail?{nail tip?}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.95,0:09:59.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.15,0:10:01.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's that doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.01,0:10:08.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About two hours ago, Kamon{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} said she\Nwas going to a nail salon and left the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.27,0:10:08.27,Signs,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.73,0:10:14.15,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It might be best not to conclude that this is suicide just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.55,0:10:18.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh, it was murder?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.49,0:10:20.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not suicide?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.18,0:10:21.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.25,0:10:25.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On the end of the stick-on nail Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} found, there were slight traces of skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.56,0:10:29.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means that what was on that stick-on nail
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.90,0:10:36.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,most likely is the skin of someone who attacked her next to her car.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.72,0:10:39.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Who was it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.37,0:10:41.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who killed Hatsune?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.84,0:10:46.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You are Raita Bamba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, who was engaged to Kamon{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.79,0:10:48.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.67,0:10:51.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How did you injure your hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.41,0:10:55.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is from when I fell on broken shards of a glass earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.65,0:10:59.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, do you remember this hairbrush?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.82,0:11:02.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, yeah, it's mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.39,0:11:05.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought it was in my travel suitcase though.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.32,0:11:09.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, it was in your suitcase,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.05,0:11:11.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,in the boot of the car that was set on fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.24,0:11:14.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just to be sure, we had hair DNA
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.80,0:11:18.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,collected from this hairbrush analysed,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.12,0:11:21.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and compared with the skin DNA on her stick-on nail.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.95,0:11:23.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're a rough match.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.59,0:11:24.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.43,0:11:25.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.40,0:11:32.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-What're you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.95,0:11:35.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you trying to say that I did it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.00,0:11:38.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it's still not an exact match,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.40,0:11:42.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so we would like your consent\Nto do a proper check.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.69,0:11:44.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop joking around!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.45,0:11:46.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Calm down, Bamba.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.22,0:11:47.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You didn't do it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.74,0:11:49.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O-Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.05,0:11:53.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Although, it would've be possible for him to have hit at me and gotten injured on purpose
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.20,0:11:58.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,in order to camouflage scratches from her resisting, wouldn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.50,0:12:00.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-What the hell did you just say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.66,0:12:02.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hm, well said.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.72,0:12:05.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Couldn't you have killed the woman you loved
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.66,0:12:08.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,before she could become someone else's, waiter?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.97,0:12:09.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.30,0:12:13.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hold on, what do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.75,0:12:16.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he won't say it himself then I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.30,0:12:21.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This guy is a lover of Hatsune's,\Nwho's been secretly seeing her!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.98,0:12:25.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?! Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.64,0:12:28.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How about it? Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.50,0:12:31.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I {\i1}did{\i0} meet her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.08,0:12:36.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that's because she hired me as a private eye...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.21,0:12:40.00,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Tōru Amuro (29)\NDetective
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.47,0:12:40.00,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I'm a detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.85,0:12:42.20,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A... detective?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.01,0:12:49.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A... detective?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.72,0:12:51.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you find it strange?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.94,0:12:59.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How come the detective Hatsune hired just {\i1}happens{\i0} to be a waiter at our marriage party?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.34,0:13:01.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.38,0:13:08.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I arranged for the party to be held at this restaurant, where I work part-time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.50,0:13:10.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why on earth?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.16,0:13:13.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, it was so I could watch your movements.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.70,0:13:15.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Watch me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.79,0:13:18.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. I did so at Hatsune{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s request.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.64,0:13:23.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She asked me to investigate and keep watch on whether or not you, possessing flirtatious tendencies, were seeing anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.80,0:13:27.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I purposefully stained your pants with cake,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.76,0:13:30.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so that you couldn't make advances on a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.26,0:13:35.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Although Hatsune{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} herself cannot testify that she asked me to do that
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.54,0:13:41.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,because she burned to death inside a car in this restaurant's parking lot,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.04,0:13:48.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,it seems that the man in sunglasses there can testify that I received the request from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.15,0:13:55.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He happened to be there when I was reporting to her the progress of my background check on Bamba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.70,0:13:57.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who on earth are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.85,0:13:58.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.90,0:14:01.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's probably another detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.93,0:14:03.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,D-Detective?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.24,0:14:07.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His client is Bamba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, the groom.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.39,0:14:11.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He thought she was seeing someone recently, so he asked the detective to find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.76,0:14:15.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The detective located their secret meeting place,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.40,0:14:19.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but the man she met was wearing a hat and a hood, so he couldn't identify him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.72,0:14:24.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the voice of the man he heard at that time resembled that of mine, a waiter,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.00,0:14:27.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so he called me to his table and ordered something.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.45,0:14:35.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After confirming that the voices were the same, he most likely sent a sign to Bamba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} that I was indeed the same man.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.41,0:14:40.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right before that, he called Bamba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and told him to come to the toilet
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.28,0:14:45.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so that he could tell him that the man in question might be in the restaurant, and he intended to find out for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.80,0:14:46.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.80,0:14:48.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.67,0:14:52.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't think you'd be a detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.44,0:14:54.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I tried to tail you, you gave me the slip.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.41,0:15:03.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, Bamba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, you were trying to marry her even though you knew she was meeting a mysterious man?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.93,0:15:05.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't you have asked her yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.96,0:15:10.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The detective said he hadn't seen the man since that secret meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.32,0:15:16.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides, I thought she'd hate me if she knew that I had hired a detective to investigate her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.91,0:15:20.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We were in a relationship where we had confessed to each other that we were both adopted.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.54,0:15:24.04,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The "same history" that Bamba{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10} talked about...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.61,0:15:30.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you'd have asked me, I would've found out right away that this nice guy's a detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.27,0:15:31.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How could I ask you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.85,0:15:34.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're famous and have a well-known face.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.31,0:15:37.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And besides, I was planning on introducing you to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.41,0:15:42.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But still... If you'd have left it to me,\Nshe wouldn't have committed suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.53,0:15:46.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What caused her to set herself on fire
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.90,0:15:52.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,might've been the fact that this guy tattled to her that you were having a wild party.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.40,0:15:54.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-I never made such a phone call.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.66,0:15:58.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides, I don't think she'd commit suicide
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.80,0:16:02.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,just from hearing on the phone that he was drunk and playing with women.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.27,0:16:03.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Speaking of phones...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.50,0:16:09.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bamba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, it seems that that you received a call that suggested suicide from her
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.46,0:16:12.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,right before the car went up in flames, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.55,0:16:15.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah... She said "goodbye" while crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.98,0:16:17.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.32,0:16:18.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-If you don't believe me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.21,0:16:22.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, tonight at 8:54!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.64,0:16:24.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's in the call history.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.64,0:16:25.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you'll allow me to have a look...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.43,0:16:29.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When did 110 receive the report?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.84,0:16:32.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see... It was at 9:21.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.41,0:16:36.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a gap of about 30 minutes, isn't there...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.01,0:16:37.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,D-Don't ask me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.41,0:16:38.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um, about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.66,0:16:41.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was the one who made the report.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.30,0:16:45.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I called an ambulance and a fire\Nengine first, and that took some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.29,0:16:50.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But by the time the ambulance and the fire engine arrived, it was too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.94,0:16:53.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The inside of the car was irrecoverably burnt.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.24,0:16:55.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But don't you find it strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.30,0:17:02.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The part of a car people ride in is usually made out of something that's hard to burn, so why did it burn so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.18,0:17:03.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.71,0:17:06.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There were some explosions from time to time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.05,0:17:09.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, those were from spray cans.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.03,0:17:12.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There were a lot of spray cans, paper, and cardboard in the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.75,0:17:14.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what ignited.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.19,0:17:16.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why were things like that in your car?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.85,0:17:23.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After the party was over tonight, we were planning to use pattern paper and spray paint to decorate the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.19,0:17:30.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We thought we'd surprise everyone by showing up at the wedding in the decorated car together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.75,0:17:32.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you don't believe me then look at the e-mail!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.85,0:17:36.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's an e-mail from her saying she's got everything we needed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.57,0:17:45.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tonight at 8:18, there was an e-mail from her saying that she'd be back in 30 minutes, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.27,0:17:50.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah. She sent a picture message from the nail salon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.34,0:17:56.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means you knew there was a large amount of flammable materials in the car
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.40,0:18:00.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,as well as the time she was coming back to this restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.05,0:18:01.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.40,0:18:06.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey... What're you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.29,0:18:09.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm saying that you could have secretly\Nslipped out of the restaurant,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.95,0:18:14.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,ambushed her in the parking lot, knocked her unconscious, shoved her into the car,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.35,0:18:16.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,set it on fire, and burnt her to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.80,0:18:18.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.02,0:18:23.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On top of that, one of the stick-on nails that she had just put on tonight had fallen near the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.42,0:18:28.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A very small amount of skin was stuck on the tip of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.03,0:18:29.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.31,0:18:38.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a high possibility that that skin got there when she was attacked by you, resisted, and then scratched you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.03,0:18:45.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The skin DNA roughly matched the hair DNA on your hairbrush.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.37,0:18:48.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,B-But, it's not like it was an exact match, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.23,0:18:51.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Say something too, Mouri!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.60,0:18:56.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I believe that "roughly" means that the skin left on that nail was contaminated
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.95,0:19:01.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,by rain, dirt, or the like, and that\Ncomplete data wasn't able to be taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.97,0:19:04.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When comparing the genome of people who aren't blood relatives,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.78,0:19:07.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,a rough match of genetic information isn't possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.72,0:19:16.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Therefore, it's natural to think that the DNA is the DNA from the same person.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.11,0:19:18.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-What the hell did you just say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.28,0:19:23.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,P-Please stop with the violence.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.53,0:19:26.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Get a hold of him, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!\NWhat if he tries to hit me again?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.95,0:19:29.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no need for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.45,0:19:30.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.20,0:19:32.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Bamba... Calm down...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.78,0:19:37.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not yet certain that the hair on that hairbrush is yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.90,0:19:41.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't it better to just let them take your DNA and check it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.30,0:19:45.30,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,They're just going to take some saliva from your mouth with a cotton swab.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.22,0:19:45.30,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}As I thought, this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.30,0:19:47.72,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Then how'd this person...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.72,0:19:49.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now then, Bamba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r},
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.58,0:19:53.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,do you permit us to do a DNA test?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.56,0:19:54.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.79,0:19:56.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then this way, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.50,0:20:05.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But aren't DNA tests amazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.58,0:20:09.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You used to only be able to tell\Nsomeone's blood type from their saliva,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.89,0:20:12.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but now you can tell for sure if two\Nsamples came from the same person.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.76,0:20:14.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.25,0:20:18.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then people who change their appearance and deceive everyone can be found out in an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.82,0:20:22.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah... Y-You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.46,0:20:26.09,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}If the results of the test come out then it'll be clear, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.32,0:20:31.52,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But if that person did do it, why is {\i1}that{\i0} still there?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.31,0:20:35.02,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Or was some kind of trick used?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.05,0:20:39.82,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}If so, why not say something about that?
