Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.00,0:22:04.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Megure.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.26,0:22:11.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a door in the back of the restaurant that leads to the parking lot,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.20,0:22:13.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but at the time of the incident it was raining hard
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.61,0:22:17.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and there didn't seem to be anyone going outside, so the door was locked.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.45,0:22:22.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then the only way to get out of the restaurant was by using the front entrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.46,0:22:27.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. But in that case I think someone would remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.00,0:22:30.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And there are no other exits?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.45,0:22:33.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can more or less get out through the window in the toilet,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.18,0:22:38.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but there's no pavement outside the window, and there's a big puddle,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.25,0:22:43.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so if you were to pass through there, footprints would've been left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.61,0:22:47.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also, it seems that the wind was\Nblowing at the time of the incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.96,0:22:52.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since the umbrella that the deceased, Hatsune{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, was carrying had flown all the way to the end of the parking lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.87,0:22:54.50,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Wind?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.50,0:22:58.83,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Come to think of it, when we came to this restaurant, the wind was blowing rather hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.55,0:23:04.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So do you detectives have any clue?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.33,0:23:06.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.02,0:23:10.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I told him that she was secretly meeting a man he was quite disturbed,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.97,0:23:16.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but recently he seemed more bothered by the fact that she's secretly been calling someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.47,0:23:21.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, she was probably talking with this guy anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.05,0:23:25.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, no... I contacted her by e-mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.48,0:23:29.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only time I've met her in public was the one time you saw me with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.48,0:23:33.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But there was one thing that seemed to upset her.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.61,0:23:35.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Upset her?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.54,0:23:36.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.76,0:23:41.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm a detective, so I thoroughly investigated Bamba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.40,0:23:43.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then, I learnt something.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.05,0:23:46.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.63,0:23:50.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was saved from the same hotel fire as Hatsune{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r},
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.60,0:23:55.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and both of them, their identities unknown, grew up in the same church.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.31,0:24:02.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...which means that as we expected...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.43,0:24:06.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can't help but think that you burnt her to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.69,0:24:07.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.56,0:24:09.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case, you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.02,0:24:10.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...not the killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.82,0:24:13.32,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And if my deduction's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.32,0:24:19.33,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}An unwelcome sad truth will be exposed.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.33,0:24:23.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On the next Conan: Wedding Eve (Part II)
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.33,0:24:30.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint: Cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.34,0:24:31.89,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,There are three detectives,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.34,0:24:31.89,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10\a1}san
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.89,0:24:33.19,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,so is it detective{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.19,0:24:34.12,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I don't like old men...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.12,0:24:36.41,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,That was terrible.
